00:38:48.400 --> 00:38:49.920
once the devil makes a move,

00:38:50.280 --> 00:38:51.520
we can find it immediately.

00:38:51.720 --> 00:38:53.600
or inform your father and Cui Wenkui immediately.

00:38:53.880 --> 00:38:54.960
to be prepared.

00:38:58.880 --> 00:38:59.960
Also,

00:39:04.840 --> 00:39:05.880
Didn't you notice?

00:39:06.600 --> 00:39:08.440
Chae Jin knows how you feel.

00:39:08.760 --> 00:39:10.200
She knew you couldn't leave me.

00:39:10.400 --> 00:39:13.600
so she asked me to stay and take care of you.

00:39:14.680 --> 00:39:16.240
But she didn't say anything.

00:39:17.120 --> 00:39:18.160
How did you know?

00:39:20.080 --> 00:39:21.720
This is the tacit understanding in battle.

00:39:22.440 --> 00:39:24.800
We don't need to talk sometimes.

00:39:27.480 --> 00:39:28.240
When can we

00:39:28.440 --> 00:39:29.800
have such a tacit understanding?

00:40:04.680 --> 00:40:05.560
It's you.

00:40:10.800 --> 00:40:11.760
Why are you here?

00:40:12.120 --> 00:40:13.040
The Japanese who came to my house.

00:40:13.280 --> 00:40:14.120
brought me here.

00:40:14.280 --> 00:40:15.480
Why did they bring you here?

00:40:16.000 --> 00:40:16.960
He doesn't trust my father.

00:40:17.600 --> 00:40:18.680
So he took me as a hostage.

00:40:19.360 --> 00:40:21.400
You took me to get vaccines today.

00:40:22.680 --> 00:40:23.920
Then come quietly.

00:40:25.120 --> 00:40:27.200
What did you do to lock me up?

00:40:28.240 --> 00:40:29.040
This is different.

00:40:29.640 --> 00:40:30.640
Only I am here

00:40:31.200 --> 00:40:32.360
my father will fight the Japanese.

00:40:34.120 --> 00:40:35.120
Good boy.

00:40:35.840 --> 00:40:38.120
What about you? Why are you here?

00:40:40.120 --> 00:40:41.120
The Japanese sent

00:40:41.200 --> 00:40:43.280
to Shaanxi.

00:40:43.680 --> 00:40:45.400
I came here hoping to find the medicine.

00:40:45.680 --> 00:40:48.560
There were many patients just now.

00:40:49.640 --> 00:40:50.960
Wu Zhen and the others are over there.

00:40:51.120 --> 00:40:52.440
They're here too.

00:40:54.600 --> 00:40:55.280
Great!

00:40:56.840 --> 00:40:58.280
We should've killed them all!

00:40:58.760 --> 00:40:59.960
They're not human.

00:41:01.960 --> 00:41:02.800
They will.

00:41:07.680 --> 00:41:08.520
How is it?

00:41:09.240 --> 00:41:10.240
Have you found my son?

00:41:10.320 --> 00:41:12.000
Master, they entered Luoyang City.

00:41:12.280 --> 00:41:14.040
We lost them.

00:41:14.440 --> 00:41:15.720
A bunch of losers.

00:41:17.120 --> 00:41:18.760
A bunch of losers!

00:41:20.640 --> 00:41:21.400
Master!

00:41:21.640 --> 00:41:22.480
Get lost!

00:41:22.720 --> 00:41:23.720
Get lost!

